Drush ( a Drupal command line tool)
- composer drush/drush
- chmod u+x /path/to/drush/drush && ln -s /path/to/drush/drush /usr/bin/drush 

drush dl drupal
drush si -y --db-url=mysql://root:root@localhost/namadb

